I was in charge of electrical and electronic connection of the devices that this company put into a car to convert to electric-powered, also I have developed some devices to make those electronic components work in harmony, such a device that converts the original signal from a MiniCooper gas pedal to a signal that the devices used, also I have developed a device that reads a CAN-Bus signal from a lithium battery box to show the consumed current in real-time in a generic RPM indicator, also a device who read from the battery lithium box through CAN-Bus the level of charge, in order to show this level instead the level of gasoline in the dashboard.
